original_title: The Perv Parlor / The Frat Shack Shakedown
overview: Presented by the infamous London rockabilly club The Frat Shack, this bizarre film is set in a Victorian brothel, where all manner of depravity takes place (hence the evocative title!). Music comes from Shack regulars such as Sexton Ming, Vibrasonic, Pooptones, Armitage Shanks, Diabolics and many more!
title: The Perv Parlor / The Frat Shack Shakedown
